title._content: Edwin C. Berry Testimonial Banquet, Hotel Multhnomah, Portland, Oregon, 1955

description._content: Original Collection: MSS - Urban League of Portland Image Description: Photo shows half of the head table. The minister at the head table is Father L. D. Stone, St. Philips Episcipal Church. The second person on the right of Father Stone is Dave Robinson, to the right of him is Dr. DeNorval Unthank and and Mrs. Dorothy Berry is on the extreme right. Ruth and John Holley are seen in the middle at the bottom of the photo. Willis Williams is the second person at the lower left table (facing the camera) and Mrs. Phil Reynolds is the second person from Willis Williams.
